{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·001.1", "text_original": "呦呦鹿鳴，食野之苹。我有嘉賓，鼓瑟吹笙。\n吹笙鼓簧，承筐是將。人之好我，示我周行。", "text_normalized": "呦呦鹿鳴，食野之苹。我有嘉賓，鼓瑟吹笙。\n吹笙鼓簧，承筐是將。人之好我，示我周行。", "notes": "鹿鳴 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·001.2", "text_original": "呦呦鹿鳴，食野之蒿。我有嘉賓，德音孔昭。\n視民不恌，君子是則是傚。我有旨酒，嘉賓式燕以敖。", "text_normalized": "呦呦鹿鳴，食野之蒿。我有嘉賓，德音孔昭。\n視民不恌，君子是則是傚。我有旨酒，嘉賓式燕以敖。", "notes": "鹿鳴 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-001__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-001", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·001.3", "text_original": "呦呦鹿鳴，食野之芩。我有嘉賓，鼓瑟鼓琴。\n鼓瑟鼓琴，和樂且湛。我有旨酒，以燕樂嘉賓之心。", "text_normalized": "呦呦鹿鳴，食野之芩。我有嘉賓，鼓瑟鼓琴。\n鼓瑟鼓琴，和樂且湛。我有旨酒，以燕樂嘉賓之心。", "notes": "鹿鳴 Chinese stanza 3."}
